{"tid":1343683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察鐵路應變部隊下周日起執勤　背囊藏最新MPX衝鋒槍巡高危車站","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:38:26.000Z","uid":36128,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9076e88bf6a0486a9d7dfa1ded5339a5150e246","tid":1343683,"uid":36128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/273937/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%87%89%E8%AE%8A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%8A%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0mpx%E8%A1%9D%E9%8B%92%E6%A7%8D%E5%B7%A1%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F273937%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%258B%25A4-%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%259B%258A%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0mpx%25E8%25A1%259D%25E9%258B%2592%25E6%25A7%258D%25E5%25B7%25A1%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%258D%25B1%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25AB%2599&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=7748680d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/273937/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%87%89%E8%AE%8A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%8A%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0mpx%E8%A1%9D%E9%8B%92%E6%A7%8D%E5%B7%A1%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99</a><br />\n針對近年世界各地於鐵路系統發生的恐襲事件，警隊今年成立了一枝「鐵路應變部隊」處理港鐵突發事故，並於下周日（23日）開始在93個港鐵車站執行職務，期間會在車站大堂、列車車廂及月台維持高調巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n34名成員中，部分來自飛虎隊，他們巡邏時除了配備一把Glock 17手槍，背囊內其實藏有一枝警隊最新購入的MPX衝鋒槍，以對付兇徒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2238897/org/1da07e3b6265bb150fb5c9394440c87c.jpg/aQZpfpZeLp8LWmXJYVh8A_jGZTE5My2gcOztBnDs7QY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2238897%2Forg%2F1da07e3b6265bb150fb5c9394440c87c.jpg%2FaQZpfpZeLp8LWmXJYVh8A_jGZTE5My2gcOztBnDs7QY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=66c63382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察鐵路應變部隊下周日才開始執勤，今日模疑拘捕劫持列車的兩名恐怖份子，並救出人質。（陳晶琦攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分成員曾當飛虎隊<br />\n<br />\n34名的鐵路應變部隊人員隸屬鐵路警區，當中包括1名督察、1名警署警長、8名警長及24名警員，成員有機場特警、飛虎隊、反恐特勤隊和衝鋒隊經驗，受訓兩個月便執勤。部隊會由下周日開始，早上5時半至凌晨1時半於93個港鐵站（不包括高鐵站以及輕鐵線），特別是高危、人流多及主要的轉車站高調巡邏。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2239138/org/d35fae996cd3d0331d6b7d1b91a2fd58.jpg/KhbZznImDXpLY_9dn-jQFGBfH3YBxkHYWOqsxljqrMY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2239138%2Forg%2Fd35fae996cd3d0331d6b7d1b91a2fd58.jpg%2FKhbZznImDXpLY_9dn-jQFGBfH3YBxkHYWOqsxljqrMY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=089773b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察鐵路應變部隊成員佩備攻防裝備。（香港01製圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防彈頭盔附夜視燈 方便暗黑隧道執勤<br />\n<br />\n為配合鐵路環境獨特，部隊須在陰暗、光線不足或封閉環境下執行職務，故裝備方面，會佩戴具夜視燈的防彈頭盔、電筒、避彈衣、保護手套、防火頭套、防毒面具等；至於槍械方面，則會配備Glock 17的手槍，以及SIG SAUER MPX衝鋒槍，而SIG SAUER MPX衝鋒槍亦是香港購入後首度曝光。根據SIG官方網頁顯示，此型號屬瑞士廠商、美國生產，且對於曾接受相關槍械訓練的部隊人員，使用SIG SAUER MPX衝鋒槍會易上手。<br />\n<br />\n鐵路警區總督察吳子輝表示，即使隧道發生任何事故，部隊亦能透過裝備，快速打開車門進行救援行動。"},{"pid":"d7e505c3e40ab5d991caa719d82b3b2cd120f30b","tid":1343683,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9076e88bf6a0486a9d7dfa1ded5339a5150e246","tid":1343683,"uid":36128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/273937/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%87%89%E8%AE%8A%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4-%E8%83%8C%E5%9B%8A%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0mpx%E8%A1%9D%E9%8B%92%E6%A7%8D%E5%B7%A1%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F273937%2F%25E8%25A